      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Dance of The Fierce Flame",
        "Client": "Dame Fiorayne",
        "Description": "During our investigations in the\r\nCitadel, we noticed a curious\r\nrise in temperature, followed\r\nby a gathering of fire monsters.\r\nI\u0027m dispatching you immediately\r\nto deal with the situation! Go\r\nforth and be victorious!",
        "Target": "Slay a Teostra and\r\nhunt the remaining targets",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "La danse de la Flamme furieuse",
        "Client": "Dame Fiorayne",
        "Description": "Pendant qu\u0027on faisait des\r\nrecherches \u00E0 la Citadelle,\r\nla temp\u00E9rature a commenc\u00E9\r\n\u00E0 augmenter et des monstres\r\nde feu se sont rassembl\u00E9s.\r\nTu dois vite les \u00E9liminer pour\r\nle bien de nos recherches.",
        "Target": "Tuer un Teostra et chasser\r\nles cibles restantes",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Danza della fiamma audace",
        "Client": "Dama Fiorayne",
        "Description": "Durante le nostre indagini\r\nalla cittadella, abbiamo\r\nnotato un curioso aumento\r\ndella temperatura, seguito dal\r\nradunarsi di mostri di fuoco.\r\nEliminali subito o il nostro\r\nprogresso verr\u00E0 ostacolato!",
        "Target": "Uccidi un Teostra\r\ne caccia gli obiettivi rimanenti",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Tanz der Grimmigen Flamme",
        "Client": "Fiorayne",
        "Description": "W\u00E4hrend unserer Untersuchungen\r\nin der Zitadelle entdeckten wir\r\neinen Temperaturanstieg und\r\neine Ansammlung von Feuer-\r\nmonstern. Ich schicke dich sofort\r\nlos, um die Situation zu kl\u00E4ren.\r\nViel Erfolg!",
